data.description: Do you hate carpet? This might be the perfect home for you.  Only carpet is in the primary bedroom closet.  Large renovated home in popular Buford swim /tennis/playground neighborhood.  New highly in demand Seckinger HS.  New paint inside and outside, including ceilings.  New lvp flooring downstairs.  Hardwood and tile upstairs.  Most of the lighting has been replaced.  Vaulted great room with upgraded ceiling fan and fireplace. Primary bedroom has walk in closet, new oversized shower door, double vanities and garden tub. Tons of extra storage with utility closet off oversized garage. Newer roof and Upstairs HVAC.  House has only one neighbor so very private.  Easy access to Hamilton Mill / 85
